{"type":"message","id":"4a1547e2","parentId":"2c147ed7","timestamp":"2026-05-07T02:02:03.585Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering skill renaming options**\n\nI’m thinking about how the user wants the Thai language applied to skills. They asked if it’s possible to rename skills to Thai, but I need to clarify that internal names can't be renamed. I could create a list of skills in Thai instead. This might relate to the skill creator, where they want to rename or edit agent skills. Since it's about the current conversation, I might just need to answer without using memory.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0671f35faf9b3a0c0169fbf297259881919631c7bc5dffa330\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-_Ka-fTDLF4W1s4BfXpy-I7akcCzIGhBy7ujYYrkLTcIW2wrYm0YZXijZvAMmecEiJAfCntmb2h8iOJQK-E8uYd35fzZ_I8vVmUCRnE0ioKpTjiX9hJkrdJfoObUn4fjJRfjvq5qu0B-VXqKeCduwn_FH_RBiTySLU9v4bRSxbcrihcjfG263QOhqfKoUgF94i3Ls_F36wSRPT59kDPZr1O5_XH2DhtgHlZ_ZyIQdt3cntnIen9YAKMqJcBilRBFkYkmUOexP8X6GHLUfJwcWE7qTfd05bqP9IQjoPvJ9Ow0sudfC4rKqiBK38d_uyvAtm9RvOmp17kjqH2HDp1TMiRaHdCzeiul4p7HhMoCNKcYtBP2EY0n7c4j-ydKt15X7H7XMimUB6_oD2sv-9YexQGhNSCM8TkfROTgL48qD2OH0bzdUuWWDPVmCQdEZcy71uA54FevZlRgV4BxLEVmqxwhIqN1X1d1rUXU0OdEbGiQlEmNk9WEGiCw-hUMdXchbhkCJ1KJHyiCxggy7RuIi1hffRO2l2xEsLCoRGMhfspdELnEOztdfdFQFAuPHR1_-id25-8taNpu3AqxLuoaBe_PSnY74yAyNkWJfBtUkprF4EX0qNfEsJbTMe3jdtcCfmFXDVww2kRRNFjVjlrJZg0j9PprrucrgSoSSdQ8fh9gKPyxTQoU9ieSw_0M11GTNyY8VQcDl8RQhwq3cDdg8wa5_p0l4i1huICXZl_Dd5lJ6dkPYW3rZwhs9RLNGoFdiowmPhC5Jghi0koeCy8AmIxwTrKBElY9szd4tq73d4T4ePMiuEfYf7lBeCSYWC7_CMUvYp3IbOCowBhr_VZL1FZq2Y05xM5wAvVLJejqxNY1krG6VJjAm4ACMNsO7WpKQp0FXay4Q1s-WNhHIgrP88gHnQBnGdda8s0d_ZpenSzYyzDVRigynlSAvYcei92LTViDmLmYgn8QiLG_So3n6BvC0tKxEZUm9_vWHc9DqOYkMs7eh1JJndwVZinp6Up4QpT2l3H-cWav5XUG7ugUXqf9XPREPMR4uZY4KeNx0TdC2Ub9o4TLxNnnpO-zmzsXNQVwS6iFjk5I_zmVLD3HT64Qm3Nn4dxlI3kGSXN9sMBf0n74lUtJwqqmad2sJxVYmLbrjaZ6urjZNN1QLK32N_xNiO6zGx1_LGKz6cENtfLNIXZFydWVqN0pwdjQfgs8uYrM6LnPZBH-euWaoA-Y_cqC5JicxW7rgEMd95NsEoEC_L3HLwBF8Q_HQomowuY20pwcZH0EF27QO_u0DQoi83HJejKBi4YXlXtiQtsmlWoSqa7ZQWdONbgsI-wOvjSP2MNSz1pk56SLhYwxF58eDmMwKy-A8iSYlGYwo0m7Yax5T5kb9-MVm974VUCpZrAX4WRuGW5PYFZRWoITWyNOLPgmGw==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering skill renaming options**\\n\\nI’m thinking about how the user wants the Thai language applied to skills. They asked if it’s possible to rename skills to Thai, but I need to clarify that internal names can't be renamed. I could create a list of skills in Thai instead. This might relate to the skill creator, where they want to rename or edit agent skills. Since it's about the current conversation, I might just need to answer without using memory.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"🧑🏼‍💻ได้ครับเจ้านาย ผมแปลชื่อให้จำง่ายแบบนี้:\n\n- browser-automation = คุมเว็บ/เบราว์เซอร์\n- healthcheck = ตรวจสุขภาพเครื่อง/ความปลอดภัย\n- node-connect = แก้ปัญหาเชื่อมมือถือ/เครื่องอื่น\n- skill-creator = สร้างหรือแก้สกิล\n- taskflow = จัดการงานยาว/งานหลายขั้นตอน\n- taskflow-inbox-triage = คัดแยกข้อความ/อินบ็อกซ์\n- tmux = คุมหน้าจอเทอร์มินัลที่เปิดค้าง\n- video-frames = ตัดรูป/คลิปจากวิดีโอ\n- weather = เช็คอากาศ\n\nชื่ออังกฤษเป็นชื่อระบบภายใน แต่เวลาคุยกับเจ้านาย ผมจะเรียกเป็นภาษาไทยให้ครับ 🧑🏼‍💻","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0671f35faf9b3a0c0169fbf29adc28819185962c11d08d215d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.5","usage":{"input":669,"output":290,"cacheRead":16896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17855,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778119315186,"responseId":"resp_0671f35faf9b3a0c0169fbf294468481918babc79c3b9f30c1"}}
